WEBVTT

00:00:00.864 --> 00:00:03.096
Intrathecal medicines are delivered

00:00:03.090 --> 00:00:05.112
via a drug pump and tubing

00:00:05.110 --> 00:00:06.696
to the fluid-filled space

00:00:06.690 --> 00:00:08.528
around your spinal cord.

00:00:08.784 --> 00:00:10.464
They may be helpful for those

00:00:10.460 --> 00:00:12.352
with severe, chronic pain,

00:00:12.350 --> 00:00:14.656
or muscle spasms due to multiple

00:00:14.656 --> 00:00:17.528
sclerosis or spinal cord diseases.

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:19.592
The pump is a small disk and

00:00:19.590 --> 00:00:21.168
catheter with a battery

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:23.560
which is implanted under the skin. 

